name: SOS 5.4.3 Release
body:
Available in [Maven Central](https://search.maven.org/search?q=g:org.n52.sensorweb-server.sos%20and%20v:5.4.3).

## Change Log
* Fix GetCapabilities KVP requests with not specified `version` parametern

* Bump version.geotools from 26.0 to 26.4 (#1196, #1245, #1269, #1296)
* Bump mockito-core from 4.0.0 to 4.5.1 (#1197, #1212, #1246, #1250, #1277, #1303, #1307)

* Bump version.arctic-sea from 9.2.0 to 9.5.3 (#1200, #1252, #1254, #1265, #1305, #1308, #1312)

* None
